Welcome to the Wiki page for An Introduction to Operations Management!

This course will teach you how to analyze and improve business processes, be it in services or in manufacturing. You will learn how to improve productivity, how to provide more choices to customers, how to reduce response times, and how to improve quality Operations. 



---
Feel free to edit the content here and to create extra pages as needed. To see how to edit/create a page, see "Help" on the left navbar.

For a business to operate successfully, it has to have a scientific approach of organization through the philosophy of management.

